#{115}{}{The boss ordered us to hold a demonstration near a night club to get the word out to the public. It's the busiest street in the city. Just as he ordered, we assembled a group at the crossroads. But around the time a crowd started to gather, I was hit by a bullet. The shot was silent, and I couldn't tell where it came from. The crowd fled immediately while our guys hunkered down. Strange, I know, but it's the truth. Ask people around on the street, they'll confirm it.}
{115}{}{老板命令我们在一家夜总会附近举行示威游行，向公众宣传这个消息。这是城里最繁忙的街道。正如他所吩咐的，我们在十字路口集合了一个小组。但就在人群开始聚集的时候，我被子弹击中了。枪声沉寂，我也说不清是从哪里来的。当我们的人蹲下来时，人群立刻逃走了。奇怪，我知道，但这是事实。问问街上的人，他们会确认的。 -- The boss ordered us to hold a demonstration near a night club to get the word out to the public. It's the busiest street in the city. Just as he ordered, we assembled a group at the crossroads. But around the time a crowd started to gather, I was hit by a bullet. The shot was silent, and I couldn't tell where it came from. The crowd fled immediately while our guys hunkered down. Strange, I know, but it's the truth. Ask people around on the street, they'll confirm it.}
#{116}{}{Can you tell what weapon you were shot with?}
{116}{}{你能告诉我你中的是什么枪吗？ -- Can you tell what weapon you were shot with?}
#{117}{}{I'm afraid not. The bullet went through. But, if it helps, I was standing near the street lamp at the crossroads, next to the home of Mr. Wright.}
{117}{}{恐怕不行。子弹射穿了。但是，如果有帮助的话，我站在十字路口的路灯旁，赖特先生家的旁边。 -- I'm afraid not. The bullet went through. But, if it helps, I was standing near the street lamp at the crossroads, next to the home of Mr. Wright.}
#{118}{}{That's enough for now.}
{118}{}{现在已经够了。 -- That's enough for now.}
